channel.title: Source won't compile the client.java! Help!
channel.description:
I changed some of the stuff in the client.java in the source, and I compiled, compiler says it finished, but when i login the previous stuff shows up.
This happens to everything I try an change. Example: at first when you log on a message shows up saying: "Welcome to the server!". I changed it in the source to say: "Hello and have fun in the server!" I compiled and all but the message still says welcome to the server.
Why won't it compile? Or change to the new client.java that I updated.
Thanks.
